\textit{In this article we propose a new fractional derivative without singular kernel. We consider the potential application for modeling the steady heat-conduction problem. The analytical solution of the fractional-order heat flow is also obtained by means of the Laplace transform. }

Key words: \textit{heat conduction, steady heat flow, analytical solution, Laplace transform, fractional derivative without singular kernel}

